{
  "page": "War of the Wolves",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#B0C4DE;\">War of the Wolves</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/The_North\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The North\">The North</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Stark</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table width=\"100%\" style=\"text-align:left; background:none\">\n  <tbody><tr><td width=\"50%\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Belligerents</td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/32px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/48px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/64px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Gaven_Greywolf\" title=\"Gaven Greywolf\">Gaven Greywolf</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Notable commanders</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/20px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/40px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> The <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Winter\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of Winter\">King of Winter</a></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\">Gaven Greywolf</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>War of the Wolves</b> is the name by which singers refer to a savage conflict between <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">skinchanger</a> named <a href=\"/index.php/Gaven_Greywolf\" title=\"Gaven Greywolf\">Gaven Greywolf</a>, referencing both Greywolf's name and the Stark sigil, the <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a>. He was killed along with his kin by a King of Winter during the course of the war. This was one of the many conflicts House Stark fought in the process of establishing their hegemony over the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_of_the_Wolves&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_kings_of_winter.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Kings of Winter.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=